name: Ladybug Lashes
description:
Ruby red lashes decorated with handmade ladybug critters and red diamantes. The feathers on this pretty pair are pastel pink with a single red emu feather.  Hand decorated with love in Melbourne Australia. Full customisation options available, please use the contact form in the menu to email through your request.

With proper care your lashes should last you many many wears. Care & wear instructions included.

All lashes come in beautiful logo-embossed gold packaging, perfect for keeping your lashes safe and as a gift box.

*Our lashes are not supplied with eyelash glue. It is recommended you invest in a quality eyelash glue, Petticoats & Gallantry are looking into stocking a quality glue in the near future.

name: Rainbow Shooting Star Lashes
description:
Shooting Star Rainbow Lashes in a butterfly wing style. These ones are adorned with handmade rainbow shooting stars on a midnight black butterfly styled wing feather, also adorned with gold sequins and little gold glass beads on the tips of the lashes, you won't find these special ones anywhere else. Hand-decorated in Melbourne Australia these ones also have full customisation options available, please use the contact form in the menu to email through your request.
